        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR6t0288-start">
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:07.22+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-h" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b09-h.15">20. Uji Existence-time</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:07.933+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s1">An ancient buddha1 said:</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:12.592+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s2">There is a time to stand on top of the highest peak;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:14.165+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s3">There is a time to walk at the bottom of the deepest ocean;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:15.107+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s4">There is a time to be a three-headed, eight-armed [being];</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:15.941+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s9" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s5">There is a time to be a sixteen foot or eight-foot [buddha];</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:16.883+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s11" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s6">There is a time to be a staff or a whisk;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:18.226+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s13" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s7">There is a time to be a pillar or a lantern;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:19.2+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s15" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s8">There is a time to be Chang's third son or Li's’ fourth son;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:45:21.528+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-01.p1.s17" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s9">There is a time to be the great earth and empty sky.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:49:12.149+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s9a">"There is a time"  (uji)</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:49:12.777+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s10">in the foregoing is such that "time" is</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:49:14.729+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s11">unmistakably "existence" and "existence" is invariably "time"5</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:49:30.321+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s12">"A sixteen-foot golden body" is time;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:49:30.984+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s13">because it is time,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:49:31.512+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s14">it has time's ornate splendor and radiant light.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:56:31.759+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s16">"A three-headed, eight-armed [being]" is time;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:56:31.809+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p2.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s15">We should study this through the present twelve hours6</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:56:32.285+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p3.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s17">because it is time,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:56:33.256+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p3.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s18">it should be one with the present twelve hours7.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:45.668+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s19">Although we do not measure longness or remoteness, shortness or imminence of the twelve hours,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:46.438+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s20">...</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:47.172+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s21">we construe these as the twelve hours.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:47.916+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s22">The direction and traces of their going and coming are so obvious</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:48.567+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s23">that people never doubt them.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:49.86+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s24">Yet, though they do not doubt,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T14:59:54.445+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-02.p5.s9" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s25">this does not mean they understand....</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:41:18.538+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s33">The self array itself and embodies the entire world8;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:41:40.556+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s34">we should see that every event,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:41:43.237+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s35">every thing in this entire world is a time.9</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:43:55.523+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s36">Things do not obstruct each other,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:43:56.372+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s37">just as times do not obstruct each other.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:44:05.178+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s38">For this reason,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:44:13.403+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s39">[things] arouse the mind at the same time;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:44:13.96+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p3.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s40">they arouse time with the same mind10.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:44:33.343+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s41">This holds true for training and perfection of the Way.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:44:34.729+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s42">...</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:45:03.33+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s43">The self arrays itself and</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:45:04.643+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s44">sees itself in array.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T15:44:57.204+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-03.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s45">This is the principle of the self being time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:25:54.066+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s47">We should learn that,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:25:56.784+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s48">because of this principle,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:26:18.483+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s49">myriad phenomena and countless things exist throughout the entire earth,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:27:22.71+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s50">and that each and every particularity, be it of thing or phenomenon, exists as the entire earth.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:27:39.597+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s51">Such a consideration is the beginning of training.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:29:51.537+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s52">When we have attained this realization,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:29:55.188+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s53">every particular thing is [what is is]</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:30:20.316+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s54">and every particular phenomenon is [what it is],</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:30:22.507+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p3.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s55">regardless of our comprehension and noncomprehension of things.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:31:09.452+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s56">Because there is no other time than this very moment,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-13T16:31:09.81+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_20-04.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0045b10.s57">"existence-time" is always the entire time.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:56:52.561+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-h" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c11-h.18">Sansuikyō The Mountains-and-waters Sūtra</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:10.653+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s1">The mountains and waters of the present1</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:11.458+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s2">are the realization of ancient buddhas' Way.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:23.243+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s3">All abide in their respective dharma-situations,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:24.104+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s4">and perfect the workings of total exertion.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:39.317+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s5">Because they are of activity prior to the kalpa of nothingness2,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:40.487+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s6">they are active in the present;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:43.25+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s7">because they are of the self prior to the emergence of any incipient sign,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:57:46.737+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s8">they are free of realization.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:58:28.223+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s9">Inasmuch as the mountains' workings are high and vast,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:58:29.057+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p5.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s10">the virtuous power to ride clouds</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:58:29.934+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p5.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s11">always reaches out from the mountains;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:58:30.531+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s12">the wondrous ability to follow the wind</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T11:58:31.694+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-01.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s13">is invariably liberated through the mountains.3</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:00:52.24+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-02.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s13.1">Abbot Tao-chiai of Mt. Ta-yang4 addressed the assembly, saying:</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:00:52.937+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-02.p1.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s14">"The blue mountain always walks;</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:00:53.861+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-02.p1.s7" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s15">the stone woman at night gives birth to a child."5</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:01:35.64+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s16">The mountain is never lacking in those workings it should possess.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s17"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:01:42.43+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s18">This is why it always dwells in quiescence,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:01:43.309+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s19">yet always engages in walking.6</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:06:54.517+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s20">We must thoroughly examine</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T12:06:55.064+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-03.p3.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s21">the instruction on "always walking."</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:03.207+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p3.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s30">Because [the blue mountain] "walks," it is "permanent."7</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:15.996+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s31">Although the blue mountain's walking</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:16.707+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s32">is faster than the "speed of the wind,"8</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:31.942+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s33">"the person in the mountain"</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:32.613+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p4.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s34">can neither realize nor know it.9</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:45.943+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p5.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s35">"In the mountain"</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:57:47.569+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p5.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s36">means "a flower's blooming in the world."10</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:58:07.309+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s37">The person outside the mountain</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:58:09.133+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s38">neither realizes nor knows it.11</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:58:17.144+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p7.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s39">Those without eyes to see the mountain</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:58:19.148+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p7.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s40">cannot realize or know,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T13:58:20.175+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p7.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s41">see or hear this same truth.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:03:40.392+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p8.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s42">Those who doubt the mountain's walking</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:03:41.305+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p8.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s43">do not yet know their own walking.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:03:42.203+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p9.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s44">It is not that hey do not walk</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:04:46.44+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p9.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s45">but that they</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:04:47.967+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p9.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s46">do not yet know or understand their own walking.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:04:27.314+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p10.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s48">When they know their own walking,</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:04:49.867+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p9.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s47">...</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:05:02.086+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-04.p10.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s49">they surely ought to know the blue mountain's walking as well.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:05:13.624+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p1.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s50">In fact, the blue mountain is neither sentient</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:05:14.086+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p1.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s51">nor non-sentient.12</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:05:28.723+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p2.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s52">To entertain any doubt</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:05:29.3+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p2.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s53">about the blue mountain's walking is an impossibility.</seg>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s54"/>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s55"/>
                    <span old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s56"/>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:09:19.023+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p5.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s58">[Yet] they do not realize that they should scrutinize</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:09:36.847+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p5.s5" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s59">[not only forward walking but also] backward walking</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:09:50.485+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p6.s1" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s60">as well as walking backward.</seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2024-03-14T14:10:05.911+09:00" corresp="#KR6t0288_HZ_29-05.p6.s3" old-corresp="#KR6t0288_T_82-2582.0062c12.s61">...<!-- inserted here --></seg>
                </p>
            </div>
